<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Beautiful Day</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #74ebd5, #ACB6E5);
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            background: #ff7eb3;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1em;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #ff4e91;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <h1>🌸 Beautiful Day 🌸</h1>
    <p>Every day is a fresh start. Breathe, smile, and begin again.</p>
    <button class="btn" onclick="showMessage()">Make it Special</button>
    <footer>Have a positive and productive day!</footer>
</div>

<script>
    function showMessage() {
        alert("✨ Today is your day! Stay positive and shine! ✨");
    }
</script>

</body>
</html>
